articles.title: Starbucks union starts three-day strike at 100 stores - CNN
articles.description: About 100 Starbucks stores across America will be on strike for the next three days, as the union attempts to turn up the pressure in it year-long battle with the coffee retailer.

articles.title: Missing college student Kenny DeLand Jr. is safe in Spain, his family says - CNN
articles.description: An American college student who was reported missing more than two weeks ago in France has told relatives he is safe in Spain, his family said Friday, seemingly resolving at least part of a mystery that sparked a multinational search.
